== 赛事历史 ==
[[File:The_International_Dota_2_video_game_tournament.jpg|thumb]]

=== 2011年 ===

2011年8月1日，[[Valve_Corporation|维尔福]]宣布举办第一届DOTA2国际邀请赛，并邀请了16支队伍进行比赛，这也是DOTA2第一次在公众面前亮相，并在网上以英语、中文、德语和俄语公示。该比赛由维尔福出资建立，包括160万美元的总奖金，而比赛硬件则由[[Nvidia|英伟达]]赞助。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/01/valve-to-hold-1000000-dota-2-tournament-at-gamescom/ |title= Valve to hold $1,000,000 Dota 2 tournament at Gamescom |date= 2011-08-01 |accessdate= 2014-02-22 |first= Lucas |last= Sullivan |work= [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |archive-date= 2014-04-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140407084929/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/01/valve-to-hold-1000000-dota-2-tournament-at-gamescom/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/10/dota-2-gamescom-tournament-to-be-streamed-live-on-dota2-com/ |title= Dota 2 Gamescom tournament to be streamed live on Dota2.com |date= 2011-08-10 |accessdate= 2014-02-22 |first= Tom |last= Senior |work= PC Gamer |archive-date= 2013-11-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131123212306/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/10/dota-2-gamescom-tournament-to-be-streamed-live-on-dota2-com/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>同年8月17日至21日在科隆游戏展上进行了第一届比赛。<ref>{{cite news|last=Miozzi|first=CJ|title=Valve Announces DOTA 2 Gamescom Tournament|url=http://www.gamefront.com/valve-announces-dota-2-gamescom-tournament/|date=2011-08-01|work=Game Front|accessdate=2014-02-22|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224105535/http://www.gamefront.com/valve-announces-dota-2-gamescom-tournament/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

比赛一开始进行[[小组赛|小组赛]]，其中每四组的胜者将晋级胜者组，而其他队伍则落入败者组。之后将进行[[双败淘汰制|双败淘汰赛]]。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/17/dota-2-the-tournament-so-far/ |title= Dota 2: the tournament so far... |date= 2011-08-17 |accessdate= 2014-02-22 |first= Tom |last= Senior |work= PC Gamer |archive-date= 2014-03-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140327021713/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/08/17/dota-2-the-tournament-so-far/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>第一届比赛的决赛在乌克兰[[Natus_Vincere|Natus Vincere]]战队和中国Ehome战队间展开。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://kotaku.com/5833570/first-ever-dota-2-championship-winner-revealed |title= First Ever Dota 2 Championship Winner Revealed |date= 2011-08-23 |accessdate= 2014-02-22 |first= Jen |last= Schiller |work= Kotaku |archive-date= 2014-07-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140717223731/http://kotaku.com/5833570/first-ever-dota-2-championship-winner-revealed |dead-url= no }}</ref>最终NaVi以3-1击败Ehome夺得冠军，获得奖金100万美元；Ehome夺得亚军，获得奖金25万美元，其他8支队伍分包奖池剩余的35万美元。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.shacknews.com/article/69831/dota-2-tournament-1-million-prize-won-by-navi |title= Dota 2 tournament $1 million finals won by Na'vi |date= 2011-08-22 |accessdate= 2014-02-22 |first= Alice |last= O'Connor |work= Shack News |archive-date= 2014-08-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140808200519/http://www.shacknews.com/article/69831/dota-2-tournament-1-million-prize-won-by-navi |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2011年DOTA2国际邀请赛是2014年记录片{{Link-en|Free to Play|Free to Play (film)}}的主要内容，该记录片讲述了三位选手的职业生涯与生活。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/21/free-to-play-review | title = ''Free to Play'' review | date = 2014-03-21 | first = Brian | last = Albert | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | accessdate = 2014-01-22 | archive-date = 2014-03-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140322124133/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/21/free-to-play-review | dead-url = no }}</ref>

