维尔福在2012年5月的[[PAX游戏展|PAX游戏展]]上宣布举办第二届DOTA2国际邀请赛。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/05/11/the-international-dota-2-championships-2012-to-be-held-at-pax-prime-this-august/ |title= The International Dota 2 Championships 2012 to be held at PAX Prime this August |date= 2012-05-11 |first= T.J. |last= Hafer |work= [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |archive-date= 2014-06-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140629124413/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/05/11/the-international-dota-2-championships-2012-to-be-held-at-pax-prime-this-august/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>这次比赛在8月26日至9月2日于[[西雅图|西雅图]]{{Link-en|贝纳罗亚音乐厅|Benaroya Hall}}举行，各支队伍将在主舞台上的隔音玻璃室内进行游戏。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://kotaku.com/5940125/dota-dispatch-watching-people-play-video-games-for-16-million |title= Dota Dispatch: Watching People Play Video Games For $1.6 Million |date= 2012-09-04 |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |first= Jason |last= Schreier |work= Kotaku |archive-date= 2013-12-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131231092104/http://kotaku.com/5940125/dota-dispatch-watching-people-play-video-games-for-16-million |dead-url= no }}</ref>奖池金额仍为160万美元，其中100万美元为冠军奖金；这次比赛同样以多种语言播报。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/06/11/dota-2-international-2012-tickets-go-on-sale-tomorrow/ |title= Dota 2 International 2012 tickets go on sale tomorrow |date= 2012-06-11 |work= PC Gamer |first= Tom |last= Senior |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |archive-date= 2013-11-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131104072320/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/06/11/dota-2-international-2012-tickets-go-on-sale-tomorrow |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.vg247.com/2012/08/31/the-international-dota-2-championships-2012-begins-at-pax-prime/ |title= The International Dota 2 Championships 2012 begins at PAX Prime |date= 2012-08-31 |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |first= Stephany |last= Nunneley |work= VG247 |archive-date= 2015-01-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150111204226/http://www.vg247.com/2012/08/31/the-international-dota-2-championships-2012-begins-at-pax-prime/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

在决赛中，上届冠军Natus Vincere被中国战队[[Invictus_Gaming|Invictus Gaming]]以3-1的战绩击败。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/9/4/3291215/dota-2-international-tournament-2012-winners-round-up |title= Dota 2 International tournament 2012 winners round-up |date= 2012-09-04 |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |first= Samit |last= Sarkar |work= Polygon |archive-date= 2014-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140304004505/http://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/9/4/3291215/dota-2-international-tournament-2012-winners-round-up |dead-url= no }}</ref>2012年11月维尔福公布了一部记录整场赛事的纪录片以及对各支队伍的采访。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/11/16/dota-2-documentary-video-released-by-valve/ |title= Dota 2 - The International 2 documentary video released by Valve |date= 2012-11-16 |accessdate= 2014-03-03 |first= Evan |last= Lahti |work= PC Gamer |archive-date= 2014-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140305170542/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/11/16/dota-2-documentary-video-released-by-valve/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>
